OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after driving
OL,7,Fwith "aggressive acceleration" and
OL,8,Fusing nitrous oxide in the moments
OL,9,Fbefore killing his friend in a
OL,10,Fdevastating crash.
OL,12,FArran Donnelly, now 28, was driving
OL,13,Fthrough Stockport at "two-and-a-half
OL,14,Ftimes" the speed of other vehicles in
OL,15,FReddish when he crashed into a wall
OL,16,Fand killed Ryan Evans, 27.
OL,18,FDonnelly, of Ince Close, Heaton
OL,19,FNorris, pleaded guilty to causing
OL,20,FEvans' death by dangerous driving at
OL,21,Fan earlier court hearing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
