OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FManchester Minshull Street Crown Court
OL,7,Fheard how Donnelly was seen driving
OL,8,Fhis Audi A3 on 24 February 2024 with
OL,9,Fthree passengers when he lost control
OL,10,Fof the car on Broadstone Road before
OL,11,Fmounting a kerb and crashing into a
OL,12,Fwall.
OL,14,FDonnelly and the two passengers sat on
OL,15,Fthe left hand side of the car
OL,16,Fsurvived, but Ryan Evans died at the
OL,17,Fscene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
