OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FThe court heard the family were left
OL,7,F"torn apart" by the "sudden and
OL,8,Fsenseless loss", as Evans was days
OL,9,Faway from travelling to Thailand with
OL,10,Fhis brother when the crash took place.
OL,12,FThe four friends were on a short drive
OL,13,Fto a pub.
OL,15,FA brief video clip officers discovered
OL,16,Fon Evans' phone, shown in court,
OL,17,Ffeatured Donnelly in the driving seat
OL,18,Fwith a balloon in his mouth at around
OL,19,F5.57pm and 0.7 miles from the scene of
OL,20,Fthe crash, which took place at 5.59pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
