OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FProsecutor Fiona Clancy said witnesses
OL,7,Fdescribed seeing Donnelly using
OL,8,F"aggressive acceleration" through the
OL,9,Fresidential area with a 30mph speed
OL,10,Flimit.
OL,12,FOne witness described seeing Donnelly
OL,13,F"start to accelerate away at an
OL,14,Falarming speed, as if the accelerator
OL,15,Fhad been floored".
OL,17,FWitnesses estimated the Audi had been
OL,18,Ftravelling "at least double" the 30mph
OL,19,Flimit, estimating speeds of "around
OL,20,F70mph to 80mph" and describing the car
OL,21,Fbeing driven "like a bat out of hell".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
