OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FClancy told the court that visibility
OL,7,Fwas "clear" at the time of the crash
OL,8,Fand no defects were found in the road
OL,9,Fsurface, with police concluding that
OL,10,F"driver error" most likely caused the
OL,11,Fcrash.
OL,13,FCCTV footage showed the Audi
OL,14,Ftravelling at excessive speed along
OL,15,FBroadstone Road, and sparks could be
OL,16,Fseen emerging from the car after it
OL,17,Fhad mounted the kerb and continued
OL,18,Ftravelling along the road.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
