OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FHis front-seat passenger was seen
OL,7,F"limping badly" after getting out of
OL,8,Fthe Audi, while the passenger sat next
OL,9,Fto Evans left the car "looking dazed",
OL,10,Fthe court heard.
OL,12,FA number of passers-by tried to help
OL,13,FEvans before emergency services
OL,14,Farrived, including a retired
OL,15,Ffirefighter.
OL,17,FOfficers arrested Donnelly and they
OL,18,Fdiscovered six balloons for nitrous
OL,19,Foxide, also known as laughing gas, in
OL,20,Fthe car alongside "several large
OL,21,Fcannisters" of the gas.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
