OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FOne of the balloons was found to have
OL,7,FDonnelly's DNA on it and prosecutors
OL,8,Fsuggested the driver may have lost
OL,9,Fcontrol of the car because of his use
OL,10,Fof the class C drug, despite its short-
OL,11,Flived effects.
OL,13,FHis Honour Judge Usher said he could
OL,14,Fnot be sure the drug caused the
OL,15,Fcollision, although Donnelly's use of
OL,16,Flaughing gas was an aggravating factor
OL,17,Fduring sentencing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
