OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FHe added: "How can I be sure that he
OL,7,Fwasn't driving in the idiotic way that
OL,8,Fhe was simply because he's an idiot,
OL,9,Frather than the effects of the drug?"
OL,11,FAs victim impact statements were read
OL,12,Fout on behalf of Evans' family and
OL,13,Fclose friends, Donnelly was seen
OL,14,Fsighing, looking down, and wiping
OL,15,Ftears.
OL,17,FHe was wearing a black jacket, white
OL,18,Fshirt, and black tie in the dock.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
