OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FEvans' dad, John Evans, said his
OL,7,F"lovely" eldest son would "do anything
OL,8,Ffor you if he could," while his Mum,
OL,9,FEloise Mckeown described his
OL,10,F"beautiful personality".
OL,12,FShe added: "I would give literally
OL,13,Fanything just to have a few minutes
OL,14,Fwith him to know he's OK."
OL,16,FDefending, Hunter Gray said Donnelly
OL,17,Fhad no previous convictions, a clean
OL,18,Fdriving licence and had recently
OL,19,Fbecome a father.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
