OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FIn a letter read by Gray in court,
OL,7,FDonnelly told Evans' family: "I know
OL,8,Fthat nothing I can say can ease the
OL,9,Fpain that I have caused.
OL,11,F"I just want you to know how truly
OL,12,Fsorry I am for the hurt and suffering
OL,13,FI have brought into your lives."
OL,15,FDonnelly has been sentenced to six
OL,16,Fyears and nine months in prison, which
OL,17,Fhe will serve up to half behind bars
OL,18,Fand the remainder on his licence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
