OL,3,CMan 'driving on laughing gas' jailed
OL,4,Cfor killing friend
OL,6,FHe was also handed a driving ban
OL,7,Ftotalling eight years and four months,
OL,8,Fprior to a mandatory retest.
OL,10,FIn sentencing, Judge User told
OL,11,FDonnelly: "Driven dangerously by young
OL,12,Fmen like you, cars can be - as this
OL,13,Fcase sadly yet again demonstrates - as
OL,14,Fdeadly as lethal weapons."
OL,16,FDetective Constable Alex Giblin, of
OL,17,FGMP's Serious Collision Investigation
OL,18,FUnit, said: "Donnelly's actions and
OL,19,Fdriving on this day resulted in a
OL,20,Fyoung man tragically losing his life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
